  <brief_title>Comparison of NovoFine® Needles (4 mm vs. 6 mm)</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Comparative, Randomised Study With NovoFine® 4 mm Needle Versus NovoFine® 6 mm Needle in Regard to Anatomical Deposition of Sterile Air in Children and Thin Adults With Diabetes and Backflow of Test Medium (Only Adults) After Injection in Thigh and Abdomen</official_title>
