  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This trial is conducted in Europe. The aim of this investigation is to explore the safety of
      a 4 mm needle compared to a 6 mm needle when injected in children and lean adults with
      diabetes.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
